      "reason" : "MOST_DIVERSE_DAY",
      "title" : "The day you let 44 genres ride shotgun in your Volkswagen van",
      "description" : "Overnight soul and lo-fi drifted into a morning of Fleetwood Mac, Sufjan Stevens, and The Beatles. Afternoon and evening zigzagged through indie pop, hip hop, j-pop, and even a podcast cameo, never settling for one sound. 623 minutes, 164 tracks, 126 artists—your most diverse day of the year.",
