      "reason" : "BIGGEST_TOP_GENRE_DAY",
      "title" : "The day you let indie pop weave through every hour",
      "description" : "From a midnight start with “Dolphin Dance” and Fiona Apple, your night blurred into morning with The Fray, sombr, and Radiohead looping through. Afternoon brought Declan McKenna’s streak and more indie pop, before a sunset of Beach House and Mitski. 489 minutes, 140 tracks, 84 artists—your top indie pop day of the year.",
