      "reason" : "BIGGEST_MUSIC_LISTENING_DAY",
      "title" : "The day you let Charli xcx and Joe Hisaishi split the night shift",
      "description" : "From midnight to sunrise, you drifted through 894 minutes of smooth jazz, lo-fi, and a marathon of Charli xcx—“party 4 u” and “Girl, so confusing” on repeat. Afternoon brought a j-pop and anime detour before Joe Hisaishi’s orchestral soundtracks closed the loop. 325 tracks, 235 artists—your biggest music day, hands down.",
